name: Amethyst Tripping
description: Hey you! Yes you who’s searching for yet another killer NFT for your collection. Take a break from all the skullz and have a non-fungible fungi instead! This one is for you mushroom and fungi lovers out there. Don’t be shy, I know you are out there.  I hope you enjoy this mind-bending psychedelic trip of an image.  Made with my trusty digital camera and a heavy touch of Photoshop. Tweet me @fotokopid
